title: Winter Olympics 2014 Opening Ceremony - No Commentary (Russian B
description:
Cheers to the peeps who original uploaded the 1080i OBS HD FEED, the Channel One 1080i and the NTV+ 1080i.

This is IMO the superior version of the broadcast, with the editing undertaken by the creative team behind the ceremony (i.e. the Russian host broadcaster). And yes the 5th ring does open in this version. Anyway, compare this and the OBS (international - i.e. any non-Russian upload) versions and see what you think.
